32
00:09:05,956 --> 00:09:08,707
Tu je ispred, gdine.

33
00:09:15,755 --> 00:09:17,967
Vaša sluga, generale.

34
00:09:18,259 --> 00:09:20,177
Niste ocekivali da cete me videti, zar ne?

35
00:09:20,219 --> 00:09:24,471
Platio sam ti u zlatu prije tri sedmice.
