Da ih postrijeljamo?
Da, gdine.

145
00:15:51,957 --> 00:15:54,626
Te Ijude iz Meina?

146
00:16:00,340 --> 00:16:05,386
"Ovim vas ovlašcujem da strijeljate
svakog ko odbije da izvrši svoju dužnost. "

147
00:16:07,304 --> 00:16:08,973
Jesu li to sve Ijudi iz Meina?

148
00:16:09,014 --> 00:16:12,768
Da, gdine. I dobri
momci, takoðe.

149
00:16:14,978 --> 00:16:18,273
Pobuna. Mislio sam
da tu rijec koriste u mornarici.

150
00:16:22,527 --> 00:16:25,238
Krecemo u zoru.

151
00:16:27,157 --> 00:16:29,449
To je dobro vrijeme dana.

152
00:16:29,491 --> 00:16:33,162
Uvijek uživam u ovim trenucima
pred zoru.

153
00:16:34,496 --> 00:16:38,125
Kad se sve ovo završi,
to ce mi mnogo nedostajati.

154
00:16:38,584 --> 00:16:40,502
Gdine?

155
00:16:40,586 --> 00:16:43,212
Nisam mislio na borbu.

156
00:16:46,841 --> 00:16:49,510
Sada je sve u Božijim rukama.

157
00:16:50,511 --> 00:16:52,221
Prijatan dan, gdine.

158
00:16:52,263 --> 00:16:54,307
Vama takoðe.

159
00:17:05,525 --> 00:17:07,486
Generale, gdine.

160
00:17:07,527 --> 00:17:11,655
Da ih probudim, gdine?
Da ih probudim i naredim pokret?

161
00:17:11,697 --> 00:17:13,533
Ne, Moksli.

162
00:17:13,575 --> 00:17:16,327
Neka momci malo duže odspavaju.
Treba im to.

163
00:17:16,368 --> 00:17:18,496
Da, gdine.

164
00:17:44,561 --> 00:17:47,231
Zatvorenici, lijevo!

165
00:17:47,272 --> 00:17:50,859
Koliko Ijudi imamo sada
u 20. Meinškoj?

166
00:17:50,901 --> 00:17:54,612
Negde oko 250, gdine,
racunajuci i oficire.

167
00:17:54,654 --> 00:17:58,783
Kako, do vraga, da
brinemo o 120 Ijudi?

168
00:17:59,283 --> 00:18:02,203
Pukovnice, danas
ce biti vreo dan.

169
00:18:02,245 --> 00:18:06,248
Pošto mi se cini da vas je vrucina vec oborila,
hocete li jahati konja

170
00:18:06,289 --> 00:18:11,045
koga je dobro Bog dao,
umjesto što marširate po prašini?

171
00:18:11,087 --> 00:18:12,671
Ti si hodao.

172
00:18:12,712 --> 00:18:15,882
Dragi, ja sam u pešadiji
od kako si ti sjedio u školskoj klupi.

173
00:18:15,924 --> 00:18:19,635
Nakon nekoliko hiljada milja,
noge se više i ne hlade.

174
00:18:19,677 --> 00:18:22,012
Jutro, Lorens.

175
00:18:22,346 --> 00:18:24,683
Kako si?
Nekako si mi iznuren.

176
00:18:24,724 --> 00:18:27,518
Prokletstvo, Tom, ne zovi me Lorens.

177
00:18:28,561 --> 00:18:30,229
Nema smisla.

178
00:18:30,271 --> 00:18:33,523
Puškom prisiljavati
covjeka da se bori.

179
00:18:40,322 --> 00:18:43,450
Odred, naprijed!

180
00:18:45,452 --> 00:18:47,411
Mirno!

181
00:18:47,453 --> 00:18:50,622
culi ste kapetana!
Mirno!

182
00:18:50,664 --> 00:18:53,835
Straža, dižite ove Ijude na noge!

183
00:19:03,050 --> 00:19:05,471
Tražim zapovjednika
20. Meinške.

184
00:19:05,512 --> 00:19:06,597
Našli ste ga.

185
00:19:06,638 --> 00:19:09,640
To je on, u redu.
Vi ste cemberlen?

186
00:19:09,682 --> 00:19:12,351
Pukovnik cemberlen za vas.

187
00:19:13,643 --> 00:19:15,395
Kapetan Bruer, gdine.

188
00:19:15,437 --> 00:19:17,981
118. pensilvanijska.

189
00:19:18,356 --> 00:19:21,944
Ako ste vi komandant,
predstavljam vam onda ove zatvorenike.

190
00:19:21,986 --> 00:19:23,362
I rado vam ih predajem.

191
00:19:23,404 --> 00:19:27,072
Bog zna da sam bajonete morao
koristiti da bih ih naterao da hodaju.

192
00:19:28,324 --> 00:19:31,202
Morate potpisati za njih.

193
00:19:31,869 --> 00:19:34,498
Potpiši, porucnice.

194
00:19:44,130 --> 00:19:46,508
Slobodni ste, kapetane.

195
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:50,971
Ovlašceni ste da koristite
svu neophodnu silu.

196
00:19:51,013 --> 00:19:53,348
Ako hocete da ih strijeljate,

197
00:19:53,515 --> 00:19:55,432
samo izvolite.

198
00:19:55,474 --> 00:19:58,018
Niko vam ništa nece reci.

199
00:20:02,732 --> 00:20:05,735
Rekao sam da ste slobodni, kapetane.

200
00:20:17,579 --> 00:20:21,041
Možete da idete sada.
Nece nam trebati cuvari.

201
00:20:27,921 --> 00:20:32,051
Zovem se cemberlen.
Ja sam pukovnik 20. Meinške.

202
00:20:34,303 --> 00:20:37,596
Kad ste zadnji put jeli?

203
00:20:38,472 --> 00:20:41,851
Pokušavaju nas slomiti
uskracujuci nam hranu.

204
00:20:42,309 --> 00:20:43,854
Još se nismo slomili.

205
00:20:43,895 --> 00:20:47,190
Tek malo prije su mi
rekli da stižete.

206
00:20:47,232 --> 00:20:48,733
Alarmiracu kuvara.

207
00:20:48,775 --> 00:20:51,234
Meso je možda posirovo,
ali nema vremena za kuvanje.

208
00:20:51,276 --> 00:20:55,155
Danas nas ceka dug put.
Vi idete sa nama, zato se dobro najedite.

209
00:20:55,196 --> 00:20:58,200
Smesticemo vas tamo u onoj šumici.
Narednice Tozier, postarajte se za to.

210
00:20:58,242 --> 00:21:00,327
