1096
01:32:08,124 --> 01:32:11,210
Moram tražiti drugi raspored.

1097
01:32:12,211 --> 01:32:14,712
Ne, gdine. To nece biti neophodno.

1098
01:32:14,753 --> 01:32:17,340
