01:37:28,670 --> 01:37:33,842
Ljudi su spremni i željni borbe.
Ne vidim korisnu alternativu.

1167
01:37:33,884 --> 01:37:34,968
Da, gdine.

1168
01:37:35,010 --> 01:37:37,179
Vrlo dobro.

1169
01:37:38,347 --> 01:37:40,225
Gospodo.

1170
01:37:40,767 --> 01:37:43,559
Dobro jutro svima.
Dobro jutro, gdine.

1171
01:37:43,601 --> 01:37:48,022
Longstrit ce napasti s desna
sa svojim prvim korpusom.

1172
01:37:48,356 --> 01:37:50,441
Hill ce mu pružati podršku

1173
01:37:50,483 --> 01:37:52,735
